cypher_method

Class Steganography

  • java.lang.Object
    • cypher_abstract.CypherAbstract
      • cypher_method.Steganography
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CypherInterface

    public class Steganography
extends CypherAbstract
    Hide a message in the least significant bits of an image. A byte contains 8 bits and as the color is mostly contain in the high significant bits. With this method, we can use the last bits of each byte to hide a message in the image. CAUTION : Steganography is not cryptography !
    Author:
    JHER
